    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to appeal.appeal_case. Business justification: Adjustment records are created after an appeal decision; linking to the appeal case provides audit trail and regulatory reporting of appeal-driven adjustments.' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:HealthInsurance ;
